Pre-Game Insights: France and Germany will face off in an international friendly on March 23, 2024, at the Groupama Stadium.
France comes into the match having won their Euro 2024 qualifying group with only one minor blot on their record.
Germany, on the other hand, have been devoid of competitive action since exiting the World Cup with a whimper for the second time in a row in 2022.
Didier Deschamps's France will be looking to avenge their 2-1 loss to Germany seven months ago.
